graph TD
    A[GET /take-picture Request] --> B[Initialize picture success flag as false]
    B --> C[Execute with Error Handling]
    C --> D[Log: Initiating picture capture]
    D --> E[Execute picture capture through main function]
    E --> F{Picture capture successful?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Log: Picture successfully captured]
    F -- No --> H[Log: ERROR - Picture capture failed]
    G --> I[Attempt to update URL with new image]
    H --> J[Return response with capture status]
    I --> K{URL update successful?}
    K -- Success --> L[Log: URL successfully updated with new image]
    K -- Failure --> M[Log: Failed to update URL after picture]
    L --> J
    M --> J
    J --> N[Request Complete]